il Domoraud|Domoraud]]}}}}<br>{{nowrap|{{pengoal}} [[Tchiressoua Guel|Guel]]}}<br>{{nowrap|{{penmiss}} [[Ibrahima Diomand\u00e9|Diomand\u00e9]]}}<br>{{nowrap|{{pengoal}} [[Ibrahima Bakayoko|Bakayoko]]}}<br>{{nowrap|{{pengoal}} [[Ahmed Ouattara (footballer)|Ouattara]]}}\n|align=left| [[Alain Gouam\u00e9n\u00e9|Gouam\u00e9n\u00e9]]\n|-\n| {{nts|14}}.\n| {{fb|COD|1997}}\n|align=center| [[1998 Africa Cup of Nations#Third place match|4\u20134]]\n| {{fb|BFA}}\n| {{CNone|'''4\u20131'''}}\n|align=center| 0\u20132\n|align=center| 4\u20133\n|align=right| [[Marcel Nkueni|Nkueni]]\n|align=right style=\"border-bottom:3px solid gray; vertical-align:top\"| {{nowrap|{{font color||#C3C3C3|[[Ekanza Simba|Simba]] {{pengoal}}}}}}<br>{{nowrap|[[Emeka Mamale|Mamale]] {{pengoal}}}}<br>{{nowrap|[[Mundaba Kisombe|Kisombe]] {{pengoal}}}}<br>{{nowrap|{{font color||gold|[[Dandou Selenge|Selenge]] {{pengoal}}}}}}\n|align=left style=\"border-bottom:3px solid gray; vertical-align:top\"| {{nowrap|{{penmiss}} [[Seydou Traor\u00e9|S. Traor\u00e9]]}}<br>{{nowrap|{{pengoal}} [[Firmin Sanou|F. Sanou]]}}<br>{{nowrap|{{penmiss}} [[Magan Diabat\u00e9|M. Diabat\u00e9]]}}\n|align=left| [[Ibrahima Diarra|Diarra]]\n|{{Hs|1}} [[1998 Africa Cup of Nations#Third place match|Third place play-off]]\n|{{dts|format=dmy|1998-02-27}}\n|-\n| {{nts|15}}.\n| {{fb|RSA}}\n|align=center| [[2000 Africa Cup of Nations#Third place match|2\u20132]]\n| {{fb|TUN}}\n| {{CNone|'''4\u20133'''}}\n|align=center| 2\u20133\n|align=center| 6\u20136\n|align=right| [[Andre Arendse|Arendse]]\n|align=right style=\"border-bottom:3px solid gray; vertical-align:top\"| {{nowrap|{{font color||#C3C3C3|[[Shaun Bartlett|Bartlett]] {{penmiss}}}}}}<br>{{nowrap|[[Helman Mkhalele|Mkhalele]] {{pengoal}}}}<br>{{nowrap|[[Pollen Ndlanya|Ndlanya]] {{penmiss}}}}<br>{{nowrap|[[Eric Tinkler|Tinkler]] {{pengoal}}}}<br>{{nowrap|[[John Moshoeu|Moshoeu]] {{pengoal}}}}\n----\n{{nowrap|[[Alex Bapela|Bapela]] {{pengoal}}}}\n|align=left style=\"border-bottom:3px solid 