bi Khazri|Khazri]] {{pengoal}}}}<br>{{nowrap|[[Dylan Bronn|Bronn]] {{pengoal}}}}<br>{{nowrap|[[Yassine Meriah|Meriah]] {{pengoal}}}}<br>{{nowrap|{{font color||gold|[[Ferjani Sassi|Sassi]] {{pengoal}}}}}}\n|align=left style=\"border-bottom:3px solid gray; vertical-align:top\"| {{nowrap|{{font color||#C3C3C3|{{pengoal}} [[Wakaso Mubarak|Wakaso]]}}}}<br>{{nowrap|{{pengoal}} [[Jordan Ayew|J. Ayew]]}}<br>{{nowrap|{{penmiss}} [[Caleb Ekuban|Ekuban]]}}<br>{{nowrap|{{pengoal}} [[Lumor Agbenyenu|Agbenyenu]]}}<br>{{nowrap|{{pengoal}} [[Thomas Partey|Partey]]}}\n|align=left| [[Richard Ofori|Ofori]]\n|{{dts|format=dmy|2019-07-08}}\n|-\n| {{nts|34}}.\n| {{fb|ALG}}\n|align=center| [[2019 Africa Cup of Nations knockout stage#Ivory Coast vs Algeria|1\u20131]]\n| {{fb|CIV}}\n| {{CNone|'''4\u20133'''}}\n|align=center| 1\u20132\n|align=center| 5\u20135\n|align=right| [[Ra\u00efs M'Bolhi|M'Bolhi]]\n|align=right style=\"border-bottom:3px solid gray; vertical-align:top\"| {{nowrap|{{font color||#C3C3C3|[[Ramy Bensebaini|Bensebaini]] {{pengoal}}}}}}<br>{{nowrap|[[Islam Slimani|Slimani]] {{pengoal}}}}<br>{{nowrap|[[Andy Delort|Delort]] {{pengoal}}}}<br>{{nowrap|[[Adam Ounas|Ounas]] {{pengoal}}}}<br>{{nowrap|[[Youcef Bela\u00efli|Bela\u00efli]] {{penmiss}}}}\n|align=left style=\"border-bottom:3px solid gray; vertical-align:top\"| {{nowrap|{{pengoal}} [[Franck Kessi\u00e9|Kessi\u00e9]]}}<br>{{nowrap|{{pengoal}} [[Maxwel Cornet|Cornet]]}}<br>{{nowrap|{{penmiss}} [[Wilfried Bony|Bony]]}}<br>{{nowrap|{{pengoal}} [[Max Gradel|Gradel]]}}<br>{{nowrap|{{font color||#FE8080|{{penmiss}} [[Serey Di\u00e9|Di\u00e9]]}}}}\n|align=left| [[Sylvain Gbohouo|Gbohouo]]\n|{{Hs|1}} [[2019 Africa Cup of Nations#Semi-finals|Semi-finals]]\n|{{dts|format=dmy|2019-07-11}}\n|}\n\n==Statistics==\n;Key\n*\u2020 = shoot-out in the final\n*'''Bold''' = winners that year\n\n===Shoot-out records===\n;Most shoot-outs in a tournament\n*'''4''' - 2019\n\n;Least shoot-outs in a tournament (since 1976)\n*'''0''' - 1990, 2008\n\n