}} (2006), {{fb|RSA}} (2013), {{fb|GHA}} (2015\u2020)\n\n===Taker records===\n;Most participations in shoot-outs\n*'''4''' - {{fbicon|CIV}} [[Didier Drogba]] (2006\u2020\u00d73, 2012\u2020), {{fbicon|CIV}} [[Kolo Tour\u00e9]] (2006\u2020\u00d72, 2012\u2020, '''2015\u2020''')\n\n;Most penalties scored\n*'''3''' - {{fbicon|NRA}} [[Rashidi Yekini]] (1984, 1988, 1992), {{fbicon|CIV}} [[Basile Aka Kouam\u00e9]] ('''1992\u2020'''\u00d72, 1994), {{fbicon|TUN}} [[Khaled Badra]] (1998, 2000, '''2004'''), {{fbicon|CMR}} [[Geremi Njitap]] ('''2000\u2020''', '''2002\u2020''', 2006), {{fbicon|CIV}} Didier Drogba (2006\u2020\u00d72, 2012\u2020), {{fbicon|CIV}} Kolo Tour\u00e9 (2006\u2020\u00d72, 2015\u2020)\n\n;Most penalties missed\n*'''2''' - {{fbicon|NGA}} [[Ademola Adeshina]] (1984, 1988), {{fbicon|TUN}} [[Sirajeddine Chihi]] (1998, 2000), {{fbicon|CIV}} [[Wilfried Bony]] ('''2015\u2020''', 2019)\n\n===Goalkeeper records===\n;Most participations in shoot-outs\n*'''4''' - {{fbicon|CIV}} [[Alain Gouam\u00e9n\u00e9]] ('''1992\u2020'''\u00d72, 1994, 1998)\n\n;Most penalties taken against\n*'''26''' - {{fbicon|CIV}} Alain Gouam\u00e9n\u00e9\n\n;Most penalties scored against\n*'''20''' - {{fbicon|CIV}} Alain Gouam\u00e9n\u00e9\n\n;Most penalties missed against (saves and off-target shots)\n*'''7''' - {{fbicon|NGA}} [[Peter Rufai]]\n\n===By team===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align: center;\"\n|-\n!Team!!Played!!Win!!Loss!!% Win!!Win Year!!Loss Year\n|-\n|align=left|{{fb|MLI}}||2||2||0||'''100%'''||2012, 2013||-\n|-\n|align=left|{{fb|BEN}}||1||1||0||'''100%'''||2019||-\n|-\n|align=left|{{fb|MAD}}||1||1||0||'''100%'''||2019||-\n|-\n|align=left|{{fb|NGA}}||7||5||2||'''71%'''||1984, 1988, '''1994''', 2006, 2010||2000\u2020, 2004\n|-\n|align=left|{{fb|EGY}}||6||4||2||'''67%'''||'''1986\u2020''', '''1998''', '''2006\u2020''', 2017||1980, 1984\n|-\n|align=left|{{fb|COD}}||3||2||1||'''67%'''||1998, 2015||2019\n|-\n|align=left|{{fb|CMR}}||7||4||3||'''57%'''||'''1984''', ''