{"title_page": "Miss Diva 2020", "text_new": "{{short description|Beauty pageant edition}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=May 2019}}\n{{Infobox beauty pageant\n| image          = File:Miss Diva 2020 logo.jpg\n| represented    =\n| photo          =\n| caption        =\n| photogenic     = Roshni Sharma\n| congeniality   = Nishi Bharadwaj\n| best national costume = Malashya Kashyap\n| date           = 22 February 2020\n| presenters     = [[Malaika Arora Khan]]<br> Sachin Kumbhar\n| acts           = [[Jacqueline Fernandez]]<br>[[Ishaan Khattar]]<br> Hari & Sukhmani\n| venue          = Yash Raj Studio, Andheri West, Mumbai\n| broadcaster    = [[MTV (Indian TV channel)|MTV India]]\n| entrants       = 20\n| placements     = 10\n| winner         = '''[[Adline Castelino]]'''\n| before         = [[Miss Universe India 2019|2019]]\n| next           = 2021\n}}\n\n'''Miss Diva 2020''' was the 8th edition of [[Miss Diva]] contest held on 22 February 2020. A total of twenty contestants were shortlisted from various auditions across the country. [[Miss Universe India 2019]], [[Vartika Singh]] crowned [[Adline Castelino]] as her successor. She will represent [[India]] at [[Miss Universe 2020]]. Miss Supranational India 2019, ''Shefali Sood'' crowned ''[[Aavriti Choudhary]]'' as her successor and she will represent India at Miss Supranational 2020. [[Miss Diva 2018]] Runner up ''Roshni Sheoran'' crowned ''Neha Jaiswal'' as her successor. Anntonia Porsild, [[:pl:Miss Supranational 2019|Miss Supranational 2019]] graced the event. This was the first edition of Miss Diva under ''Liva Fluid Fashion''.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.livafluidfashion.com/|title=LIVA Fluid Fashion {{!}} Birla Cellulose {{!}} Clothing by Aditya Birla Group - LIVA|website=www.livafluidfashion.com|access-date=2020-02-06}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://beautypageants.indiatimes.com/missdivaform.cms?from=mdr|title=Miss Diva: Beauty Pageant Entry Form {{!}} Apply Online for Miss Diva Beauty Contest|website=beautypageants.indiatimes.com|access-date=2019-10-11}}</ref>\n\n==Final results==\n;Color keys\n{{plainlist|\n* {{Color box|#50C878|border=darkgray}} Declared as the winner in an International pageant.\n* {{Color box|#89CFF0|border=darkgray}} Ended as Runner-up in an International pageant.\n* {{Color box|#F2CECE|border=darkgray}} Ended as finalist or semifinalist in an International pageant.\n* {{Color box|#FFFACD|border=darkgray}} Unplaced.\n}}\n{| class=\"sortable\" border=\"5\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin: 1em 1em 1em 0; background: #FFFFFF; border: 1px #aaa solid; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 90%;\"\n|- bgcolor=\"#787878\" colspan=10 hialign=\"center\"\n|align=\"center\" width=\"280\"|<span style=\"color:#FFFFFF\">'''Final Results'''</span>||align=\"center\" width=\"250\"|<span style=\"color:#FFFFFF\">'''Candidate'''</span>|| align=\"center\" width=\"300\"|<span style=\"color:#FFFFFF\">'''International Placement'''</span>\n|-\n! Miss Universe India 2020\n|\n* '''[[Adline Castelino]]'''\n| ''TBD''\n|-\n! Miss Diva - Supranational 2020\n|\n* '''[[Aavriti Choudhary]]'''\n| ''TBD''\n|-\n! Miss Diva Runner-up\n|\n* '''Neha Jaiswal'''\n|-\n! Top 5\n|\n* Anisha Sharma\n* Roshni Sharma\n|-\n! Top 10\n|\n* [[Archana Ravi]]\n* Arshina Sumbul\n* Malashya Kashyap\n* Rushali Yadav\n* Vaishnavi Ganesh\n|}\n\n=== Special Awards ===\n{| class=\"sortable\" border=\"5\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin: 1em 1em 1em 0; background: #FFFFFF; border: 1px #aaa solid; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 90%;\"\n|- bgcolor=\"#787878\" colspan=10 hialign=\"center\"\n| align=\"center\" width=\"280\"|<span style=\"color:#FFFFFF\">'''Award'''</span>||align=\"center\" width=\"250\"|<span style=\"color:#FFFFFF\">'''Winner'''</span>\n|-\n! colspan=\"2\" | Grand Finale\n|-\n| '''Miss Multimedia'''\n| [[Archana Ravi]]\n|-\n! colspan=\"2\" | Preliminary shows\n|-\n| '''Best National Costume'''\n| Malashya Kashyap\n|-\n| '''Miss Body Beautiful'''\n| Malashya K